Droid@Screen tool enables you to display your android screen on your desktop
in portrait/landscape mode and does image scaling too. 

The program is available http://blog.ribomation.com/droid-at-screen/

You can learn more about the application in this blog post.
http://playingwithsid.blogspot.com/2012/03/how-to-display-your-android-screen-on.html
